Subject: War on Cooties: Bringing Nerd Men and Women to the Same Game Board
Description: Coming back for a second year, this panel takes nerd culture by the horns and wrestles with the cold hard truth: equal gender representation in nerd culture is slim at best. We will explore the the social issues, inequality, and perks that come with being a geeky woman, but no matter your gender, please join in!  Speakers include:Victoria Stapels, April Nance, Erika Carlson - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
